    "body": "Same error here. Something is cooking on the typings. Just followed the building ui steps on algolia aaaaaand... no bueno.\r\n\r\nFollowing the typings tracks I can get to this...\r\n![Screenshot 2024-09-04 at 11 20 41 AM](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/546f9b48-a47b-4d8f-b947-8e1e5546c997)\r\n\r\n...which seems to indicate that the latest client (v5) uses the legacy search methods. Following a bit more I can see that is has been marked as deprecated...\r\n![Screenshot 2024-09-04 at 11 21 30 AM](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f966defd-5d00-4547-a862-68ffb7972d53)\r\n\r\nNot sure if the problem is that on one of the other packages...",
